<template>
  <v-header @changePage="changePage"></v-header>
  <v-main-wrapper v-if="page==1"></v-main-wrapper>
</template>

<script>
import VMainWrapper from "@/components/v-main-wrapper";
import VHeader from "@/components/v-header";
export default {
  name: "v-main-page",
  components: {VHeader, VMainWrapper},
  data(){
    return{
      page: 1
    }
  },
  methods:{
    changePage(page){
      this.page = page;
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
